@startuml
title Paper Lookup - Search Then Import Sequence
hide footbox
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor Researcher
boundary UpdateProfileView
control PaperLookupController
participant PaperLookupInputBoundary <<boundary>>
control PaperLookupInteractor
participant UserAPIGatewayInterface <<boundary>>
entity SemanticScholarGateway
collections "Semantic Scholar API" as SemanticScholar
participant PaperLookupOutputBoundary <<boundary>>
control PaperLookupPresenter
entity PaperLookupViewModel

Researcher -> UpdateProfileView: Enter author name
UpdateProfileView -> PaperLookupController: searchAuthors(name)
PaperLookupController -> PaperLookupInputBoundary: searchAuthors(inputData)
PaperLookupInputBoundary -> PaperLookupInteractor: searchAuthors(inputData)
PaperLookupInteractor -> UserAPIGatewayInterface: searchAuthors(name)
UserAPIGatewayInterface -> SemanticScholarGateway: searchAuthors(name)
SemanticScholarGateway -> SemanticScholar: GET /author/search
SemanticScholar --> SemanticScholarGateway: candidate JSON
SemanticScholarGateway --> PaperLookupInteractor: gateway candidates
PaperLookupInteractor -> PaperLookupOutputBoundary: prepareAuthorCandidatesView(candidates)
PaperLookupOutputBoundary -> PaperLookupPresenter: prepareAuthorCandidatesView(candidates)
PaperLookupPresenter -> PaperLookupViewModel: setCandidates(candidates)
PaperLookupViewModel --> UpdateProfileView: notify change
UpdateProfileView --> Researcher: Show author candidates

Researcher -> UpdateProfileView: Select correct author
UpdateProfileView -> PaperLookupController: selectAuthor(authorId)
PaperLookupController -> PaperLookupInputBoundary: selectAuthor(inputData)
PaperLookupInputBoundary -> PaperLookupInteractor: selectAuthor(inputData)
PaperLookupInteractor -> UserAPIGatewayInterface: getAuthorPapers(authorId)
UserAPIGatewayInterface -> SemanticScholarGateway: getAuthorPapers(authorId)
SemanticScholarGateway -> SemanticScholar: GET /author/{id}/papers
SemanticScholar --> SemanticScholarGateway: paper JSON
SemanticScholarGateway --> PaperLookupInteractor: publications
PaperLookupInteractor -> PaperLookupOutputBoundary: prepareAuthorImportView(author, papers)
PaperLookupOutputBoundary -> PaperLookupPresenter: prepareAuthorImportView(author, papers)
PaperLookupPresenter -> PaperLookupViewModel: setImportedProfile(author, papers)
PaperLookupViewModel --> UpdateProfileView: notify change
UpdateProfileView --> Researcher: Pre-fill metrics and papers
@enduml
